156
00:08:29,266 --> 00:08:30,891
Right. Of course they are.

157
00:08:31,110 --> 00:08:32,695
Didn't mean to doubt you or anything, it's just,

158
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,574
when I first saw them,
I kind of thought they looked a bit

159
